All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Address
    Address class represents a physical address with various components
    Admin
    The Admin class represents an administrator of a store system.
    Catalog
    The Catalog class represents a catalog of items, organized into categories.
    Checkout
    The Checkout class represents the process of finalizing an order by specifying an address for delivery.
    Customer
    Customer class - Defines a customer with various properties
    Item
    Defines an item with various properties
    Main
    This class to test Toffee Store core logic
    Order
    Defines an order with various properties
    OTPManager
    The OTPManager class generates a One-Time Password (OTP) and sends it to a specified email address.
    ShoppingCart
    ShoppingCart class - Defines a shopping cart with various properties
    Store
    Represents a store which has a name, a catalog, a list of admins, a list of customers, and a queue of orders placed by customers.
    StoreManager
    The StoreManager class handles the overall flow of the store system, including registering and logging in users, displaying the catalog of products, and managing the store (for admins).
    systemManager
    The systemManager class is responsible for managing the overall system and interacting with the store, customers, and admins.
    User
    User - Represents a user account with associated information
